		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(center)"><placeName>Evansville</placeName> <date>Apl 8. 1861</date>&#8212;</p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
				<p><placeName>Philadelphia Pa</placeName></p>
				<p>D<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Sir&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">It has been some time<lb/> since I had this pleasure&#44; but it has<lb/> not been my fault&#44; absence from home<lb/> and constant employment are the cau&#44;<lb/>ses&#59;&#8212; <del>but</del> and I hope you will par&#44;<lb/>don me.&#8212;  Enclosed I hand you a few<lb/> pages appertaining to <add>Hebrew</add> here&#44; for pub&#44;<lb/>lication in your valuable paper&#59; which<lb/> I hope you will insert&#44; but request you<lb/> at the same time to examine it&#44; if you<lb/> find any mistakes please correct&#44; I<lb/> am not a very good writer.&#8212; I am<lb/> very much pleased with the contem&#758;<lb/>plated changes of your paper.&#8212;  If<lb/> any body is owing you here at this</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>place&#44; please send me the bills<lb/> I will collect for you.&#8212; Please<lb/> send me bill of in your next fa&#44;<lb/>vour of my own <sic>intebdness</sic>&#59; which<lb/> I will promptly <sic>remitt</sic> you.&#8212;<lb/>  As I have nothing else to com<add>m</add>uni&#44;<lb/>cate at present&#59; allow me to assure<lb/> you of the high <del>esteem</del> esteem I entertain<lb/> and remain Respectfully<lb/> <sic>Truely</sic> yours</p>
				<p><persName role="author">L. M. Plant</persName></p>
				<p>Enclosed I hand you the right to<lb/> collect funds for the <add>Hebrew</add> for the pur<lb/><sic>puse</sic> to erect synagogue&#59; if you can do<lb/> any thing for her&#44; it will be <sic>duely</sic><lb/> appreciated.</p>
				<p> <persName role="author">P.</persName>&#8212;</p>
		</body>
